tes et campagnes sur les plateformes publicitaires pour d\u00e9finir un plan d\u2019action.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n    <div class=\"card card-prestation-basic\">\n    <div class=\"thumbnail\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"61\" height=\"61\" src=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/Icon-SEA-strategie.svg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Icon SEA Strategie\" \/>    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"content\">\n        <h3 class=\"titre_4\">Strat\u00e9gie Ads<\/h3>\n<p>Nous d\u00e9finissons votre strat\u00e9gie d\u2019achat m\u00e9dia sur les diff\u00e9rents r\u00e9seaux publicitaires pour optimiser les performances gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9coute de vos objectifs et la compr\u00e9hension de votre business.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n    <div class=\"card card-prestation-basic\">\n    <div class=\"thumbnail\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"61\" height=\"61\" src=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/Icon-SEA-structuration-compte.svg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Icon SEA Structuration Compte\" \/>    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"content\">\n        <h3 class=\"titre_4\">Structuration des comptes<\/h3>\n<p>Nous adaptons votre strat\u00e9gie aux exigences de chaque plateforme en mati\u00e8re d\u2019organisation, d\u2019ench\u00e8res, de r\u00e9daction d\u2019accroches publicitaires et de ciblage.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n    <div class=\"card card-prestation-basic\">\n    <div class=\"thumbnail\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"61\" height=\"61\" src=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/Icon-SEA-pilotage-campagne.svg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Icon SEA Pilotage Campagne\" \/>    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"content\">\n        <h3 class=\"titre_4\">Pilotage de vos campagnes Ads<\/